Title: RLM-Reasoning Mode (depth-first deliberate)
Description: Implements deliberate multi-step reasoning with tree-search and tool-use hooks; supports self-consistency and verifier reranking.
PlanToConvertToKyra: Transpile control-graph to Kyra IR; replace Python hooks with Kyra stdlib once stable.

Title: RLM-Regression Mode (fast heuristic)
Description: Latency-first mode using shallow reasoning, prompt shortcuts, and early-exit heuristics.

Title: RLM-Recursive Mode (divide-and-conquer)
Description: Task decomposition planner that recurses, caches subresults, and recombines with verifiers.

Title: Mixture-of-Agents Orchestrator
Description: Runs multiple specialized agents; ballot/rerank via confidence-weighted majority with diversity penalties.

Title: Graph-of-Thoughts Planner
Description: Builds a DAG of subproblems; schedules with budget-aware search.

Title: Agent Memory OS (Mem-tiered)
Description: Tiered memory (short-term, episodic, semantic); eviction, summarization, and cross-session identity.

Title: GraphRAG Service
Description: Ingests docs into entity/relation graph; query expansion, subgraph reasoning and citations.

Title: Speculative Decoding Engine
Description: Draft-and-verify/multi-lookup speculative sampler; pluggable draft models; compatible with vLLM.

Title: vLLM Adapter + PagedAttention
Description: Adapter to run local/remote vLLM; exposes batch APIs, paged KV, tensor parallel settings.

Title: FlashAttention-3 Guarded Kernels
Description: Optional FA-3 paths on supported GPUs; CPU/HIP fallback with feature flags.
PlanToConvertToKyra: Lift kernels to Kyra accel API.

Title: KV Cache NVMe Tier & Compression
Description: Paged KV spill to NVMe with segment pinning; support quantized KV and eviction.

Title: Structured Output Validator
Description: Schema-enforced outputs with JSON Schema; automatic repair and delta patches.

Title: DPO/RLAIF Training Harness
Description: Preference datasets, DPO variants, offline RLAIF; trainer + eval suites.

Title: Self-Rewarding / Test-Time Learning Kit
Description: Test-time training hooks & self-evaluation loops for domain adaptation.

Title: Prompt & Context Compression
Description: Learned & rule-based prompt compression; KV compaction; recap prompts.

Title: Session Graph Recorder
Description: Event DAG of tasks/tools/results for replay, audits, and learning.

Title: Multi-Agent Social Dynamics Harness
Description: Simulate agent swarms to detect norm formation, drift, and bias; inject guardrails.

Title: KyraMojo/MLIR Bridge (exploratory)
Description: Prototype mapping from Kyra IR to MLIR dialects; kernel lowering hooks.

Title: Function-Calling Tool Router 2.0
Description: Unified router supporting OpenAI-style tool calls + local adapters; schema-first.
